Package: statart
Title: Use Stata-like functions in tidyverse
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Minghong", "Shen", , "mhshenaa@connect.ust.hk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of starter-friendly, Stata-like functions for exploring the art of statistics using R. Functions like `tab()`, `tab1()`, `fre()`, `summ()`, and `codebook()` are included.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
